==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[Oxford]] [[comma]]'''
# (countable) The comma preceding a [[conjunction]] in a [[list]] of three or more items.

===Example===
*''(non-standard):'' With an Oxford comma: ''red, green, yellow, and blue''
*Without an Oxford comma: ''red, green, yellow and blue''

===Alternative spellings===
*[[Serial comma]]
*Sometimes known as the [[Harvard comma]] in the US.